| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5279 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 739941f5-acbc-5c11-9b7f-fa32c07f6129"
